  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"syhMFayv\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=680112224&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%9F%83%E9%9A%86%C2%B7%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">埃隆·马斯克<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>（Elon Musk）的大“女儿”<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=680112224&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%96%87%E8%96%87%E5%AE%89%C2%B7%E7%8F%8D%E5%A8%9C%C2%B7%E5%A8%81%E5%B0%94%E9%80%8A&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">薇薇安·珍娜·威尔逊<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>公开驳斥了她的父亲最近对她发表的关于反跨性别言论。</p><p data-pid=\"n3Y0xe0U\">薇薇安原名<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=680112224&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%B3%BD%E7%BB%B4%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">泽维尔·马斯克<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，曾经是这位世界首富的的儿子。但在年满18岁之际，这个孩子选择成为一名跨性别者，并改姓为薇薇安。择成为一名跨性别者，并改姓为薇薇安。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ac6013b616828234d99d1132aa2daa3d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"365\" data-original-token=\"v2-7fee7c21e9c77f62b3528dc146ed28e7\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d41d33e05d4741ad0b4fd56b29e41f7e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ac6013b616828234d99d1132aa2daa3d_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ac6013b616828234d99d1132aa2daa3d_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"365\" data-original-token=\"v2-7fee7c21e9c77f62b3528dc146ed28e7\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d41d33e05d4741ad0b4fd56b29e41f7e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ac6013b616828234d99d1132aa2daa3d_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ac6013b616828234d99d1132aa2daa3d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"365\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"-6IQ35XA\"><br>马斯克周一发帖称，薇薇安“天生是同性恋，有轻微自闭症”。为此他补充了证据，回忆当薇薇安还是一个孩子，她会“为我挑选夹克，还会称赞“太美妙（fabulous，被认为是男同性恋者常用的词汇）了”，</p><p data-pid=\"Ld-KUEtX\">面对父亲的敌意，20岁的薇薇安毫不示弱，回应他的描述是不真实的同性恋刻板印象。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d3126869a3781ca60810e2774f5ac01a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"428\" data-original-token=\"v2-896410b5ec532834bd1aa6a7a03d68da\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-87b4f32fa7bc74dc0ec748f5211a507e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d3126869a3781ca60810e2774f5ac01a_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d3126869a3781ca60810e2774f5ac01a_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"428\" data-original-token=\"v2-896410b5ec532834bd1aa6a7a03d68da\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-87b4f32fa7bc74dc0ec748f5211a507e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d3126869a3781ca60810e2774f5ac01a_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d3126869a3781ca60810e2774f5ac01a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"428\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div></figure><p><br><br></p><p data-pid=\"RlSWzo5_\">“我从来没有为他挑选过夹克，我肯定不会称它们太美妙了……我四岁时就再没有使用美妙这个词，我要再次重申......我当时四岁。“薇薇安强调。</p><p data-pid=\"nM0ABbfs\">她补充：“（马斯克）不知道我小时候是什么样子，因为他根本不在我身边，在跟他的那里的一小段时间里，我因为我的女性气质和古怪个性而受到无情的骚扰。”</p><p data-pid=\"ZNBlxjeV\">2022 年，薇薇安向加州法院申请更改她的名字和性别，称她不再希望“以任何方式、形式或形式”与父亲有关系。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9295dcff80c9eeba6978616a29dce59_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"617\" data-rawheight=\"793\" data-original-token=\"v2-85ae01726b8fa16114681b1e7fc50a6a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5529963eaa8fc01480c5d46ecc683f70_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"617\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a9295dcff80c9eeba6978616a29dce59_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='617' height='793'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"617\" data-rawheight=\"793\" data-original-token=\"v2-85ae01726b8fa16114681b1e7fc50a6a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5529963eaa8fc01480c5d46ecc683f70_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"617\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a9295dcff80c9eeba6978616a29dce59_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9295dcff80c9eeba6978616a29dce59_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p><br><br></p><p data-pid=\"fMX0LoAe\">美联社称，近年来，马斯克越来越迷恋右翼政治，他经常在社交媒体上分享反移民、反跨性别的帖子。</p><p data-pid=\"mABMxwN-\">本周一，马斯克接受了加拿大右翼播客乔丹·彼得森的采访，声称自己被“欺骗”签署了儿子的变性医疗文件。这位亿万富翁说，在儿子转变为薇薇安后，他“发誓要摧毁觉醒的心灵病毒”。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-81d1bf1b7705872b6c47c9d2f3354037_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"360\" data-original-token=\"v2-eff086037cc3aeca36c649f1630c1b2f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-628b057bb7fb5e78b2d598747997deeb_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-81d1bf1b7705872b6c47c9d2f3354037_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='640' height='360'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"360\" data-original-token=\"v2-eff086037cc3aeca36c649f1630c1b2f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-628b057bb7fb5e78b2d598747997deeb_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-81d1bf1b7705872b6c47c9d2f3354037_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-81d1bf1b7705872b6c47c9d2f3354037_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p><br><br></p><p data-pid=\"5QfYMaXO\">在彼得森的采访中，马斯克认为他的孩子在变性后“死了”，并且坚持薇薇安不是女孩。</p><p data-pid=\"QNmuFCXH\">其实从某种程度来说，马斯克能够被大家理解，好好的一个儿子说变性就变性，对于他来说冲击一定不小。但正如薇薇安所说，马斯克也要反思自己有没有尽到一个父亲的责任，养育11个孩子的他，究竟能花多少时间陪伴家人呢？</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1efe5fa34f9d88d24965d2947e945d8a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"474\" data-rawheight=\"753\" data-original-token=\"v2-5d4679117423522a9740219a5503d292\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a5430db632d0d642197758f202e75a5c_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"474\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1efe5fa34f9d88d24965d2947e945d8a_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='474' height='753'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"474\" data-rawheight=\"753\" data-original-token=\"v2-5d4679117423522a9740219a5503d292\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a5430db632d0d642197758f202e75a5c_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"474\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1efe5fa34f9d88d24965d2947e945d8a_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1efe5fa34f9d88d24965d2947e945d8a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
